---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: null
description: Brady Redfearn builds AI products and the governance to back them up. 16+ years shipping systems in the rooms where legal, security, and the board all get a vote.
ogSlug: home
---
<section class="hero">
  {% include "partials/ambient-log.njk" %}
  <div class="wrap" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
    <div class="live-badge" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <span class="live-dot"></span> Open to Senior Technical Product Manager conversations
    </div>
    <h1>AI Systems That Ship,<br>and Hold Up Under Scrutiny.</h1>
    <p class="hero__lead">
      I build AI products and the governance to back them up. Sixteen years shipping systems other people
      were still arguing about. PhD in Systems Engineering. I take the jobs nobody else wants.
    </p>
    <div class="hero__ctas">
      <a href="/work/" class="btn btn-primary">View Full Work &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-ghost-dark">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__credentials">
      <div class="hero__credential">
        <div class="value">16+</div>
        <div class="label">Years in AI &amp; Product Leadership</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__credential">
        <div class="value">PhD</div>
        <div class="label">Systems Engineering</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__credential">
        <div class="value">$45M</div>
        <div class="label">Portfolio Scope Led</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__credential">
        <div class="value">$51B</div>
        <div class="label">In Proposal Value Authored</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section wrap">
  <div class="split-cta">
    <div class="split-cta__panel is-primary">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="color: rgba(247,244,239,0.5);">Evaluating me for a role</div>
      <h2>I want a bigger platform to run AI on. Not a bigger title.</h2>
      <p>Senior technical product leadership, somewhere with the scale and resources to build AI systems that actually hold up. Track record's below.</p>
      <a href="/work/" class="btn btn-ghost-dark">View Full Work &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="split-cta__panel">
      <div class="eyebrow">Need AI built or governed</div>
      <h2>Redfearn Group takes the engagement your team is stuck on.</h2>
      <p>AI strategy. LLM agent architecture. Governance frameworks that satisfy legal without slowing engineering down.</p>
      <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="btn btn-ghost">Email {{ site.email }} &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--border-top">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="section-label">Track Record</h2>
    <div class="metrics">
      <div>
        <div class="metric__value">$45M</div>
        <div class="metric__label">Portfolio Scope Managed</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="metric__value">$51B</div>
        <div class="metric__label">In Proposal Value Authored</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="metric__value">75<span class="unit">x</span></div>
        <div class="metric__label">SaaS Adoption Scaled</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="metric__value">$750K</div>
        <div class="metric__label">Research Funding Secured</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="metric__value">200<span class="unit">+</span></div>
        <div class="metric__label">Students Mentored</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--border-top">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-label">When It Gets Hard</div>
    <h2>The work nobody else wanted to own.</h2>
    <div class="card-grid" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Federal &amp; Defense</div>
        <h3>Directing a $45M portfolio where compliance isn't optional</h3>
        <p class="small">Six government contract portfolios, one product strategy. The proposals had to survive a review board that's heard every promise before.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Program Building</div>
        <h3>Raising $325K for a lab that didn't exist yet</h3>
        <p class="small">No budget, no space, no track record. Won the first sponsored capstone on the pitch alone. Everything after that got easier.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Enterprise SaaS</div>
        <h3>Scaling adoption 75x when the instinct was to spend on marketing</h3>
        <p class="small">The usability problem was inside the product. No amount of marketing spend would have touched it. The growth loop data made that case on its own.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="eyebrow">Defense &amp; Product Strategy</div>
        <h3>Launching two prototypes on time and under budget when the ask was to invent the business case first</h3>
        <p class="small">Secured $750K in research funding, building the case from nothing. Shipped both prototypes under budget, on time, and to compliance and client standards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--border-top">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-label">Featured Work</div>
    <h2>Case studies, not slideware.</h2>
    <div class="card-grid content-layer" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
      {% for cs in collections.caseStudies | limit(3) %}
      <a href="{{ cs.url }}" class="card">
        <div class="eyebrow">{{ cs.data.themes[0] }}</div>
        <h3>{{ cs.data.title }}</h3>
        <p class="small">{{ cs.data.description }}</p>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;"><a href="/work/" class="btn btn-ghost">See the full case study library &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

