      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M16 4 L26 8 V15 C26 22 21.5 26.5 16 28.5 C10.5 26.5 6 22 6 15 V8 Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M11 15.5 L14.5 19 L21.5 11.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg></div>
        <h3>AI Governance &amp; Compliance</h3><p class="small">NIST-aligned frameworks that enable shipping instead of blocking it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="16" cy="7" r="3" fill="currentColor"/>
          <path d="M16 10 V15 M16 15 L8 15 L8 22 M16 15 L16 22 M16 15 L24 15 L24 22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <circle cx="8" cy="24.5" r="2.5" fill="currentColor"/>
          <circle cx="16" cy="24.5" r="2.5" fill="currentColor"/>
          <circle cx="24" cy="24.5" r="2.5" fill="currentColor"/>
